for the needles to paralyze you.

215
00:22:44.527 --> 00:22:47.194
Then eats you
while you can't move.

216
00:22:47.329 --> 00:22:49.697
(GROANS. ROARS. CLICKING)

217
00:22:54.636 --> 00:22:58.541
I could help you. but...
I need a hand.

218
00:22:59.438 --> 00:23:01.544
(CHUFFS. GRUNTS)

219
00:23:03.012 --> 00:23:05.240
(GRUNTS)

220
00:23:05.642 --> 00:23:07.911
(IN YAUTJA)

221
00:23:08.047 --> 00:23:12.086
Yautja might hunt alone.
but they die alone too.

222
00:23:12.222 --> 00:23:14.425
(CHITTERING. GRUNTING)

223
00:23:15.126 --> 00:23:17.351
-Kalisk.
-(WHICKERS)

224
00:23:20.191 --> 00:23:22.864
-You're hunting the Kalisk.
-(METALLIC CLANG)

225
00:23:23.000 --> 00:23:24.766
(SHRIEKS)

226
00:23:24.902 --> 00:23:26.261
(THUD)

