00:23:30.073 --> 00:23:31.234
(ROARS ANGRILY)

229
00:23:31.370 --> 00:23:32.436
(GRUNTS)

230
00:23:32.571 --> 00:23:33.840
(THORNS RICOCHETING)

231
00:23:34.804 --> 00:23:36.370
