232
00:23:38.345 --> 00:23:39.748
(GRUNTS. GASPS)

233
00:23:39.884 --> 00:23:41.617
(ROARS)

234
00:23:43.683 --> 00:23:45.381
THIA: It happens fast. huh?

235
00:23:45.517 --> 00:23:47.216
(PANTING)

236
00:23:47.351 --> 00:23:50.054
THIA: If you had a weapon.
you know. I could use it.

237
00:23:50.588 --> 00:23:52.386
(BEEPING)

238
00:23:54.358 --> 00:23:56.363
THIA: Throw me that.
and I can get you the antidote.

239
00:23:56.499 --> 00:23:58.902
-(BREATHING HEAVILY)
-(SHRIEKS)

240
00:23:59.037 --> 00:24:00.262
THIA: Now or never.

