-(SQUEALING)

250
00:24:37.976 --> 00:24:39.906
(PANTING) Hi.

251
00:24:43.445 --> 00:24:45.813
(SPEECH IN YAUTJA ECHOES)

252
00:24:48.746 --> 00:24:50.587
(BREATHING DEEPLY)

253
